**Describe your issue**

Hi,

It seems components cannot have utilities such as md:, lg: or dark: applied to it. For instance, I defined a button.css file:
```
@layer components {
   .btn {
        @apply
            inline-flex items-center justify-center
            gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 font-semibold text-base text-white
            rounded-xl border-1 border-white/40 select-none
            focus:outline-4 focus:outline-blue-800/80 focus:outline-offset-2;
   }
   .btn-lg {
         @apply text-lg px-5 py-2;
   }
}

// Then using it as follows does not work, the btn-lg is not applied on medium and up:
<button class="btn md:btn-lg">Click Me</button>
```

On a different nuxtjs project with tailwind v3 everything is working as expected.

Thanks for you help

